data.name: label3.Text
data.value: All projects will be migrated to the selected Studio destination version. Please select the projects you would like to move into destination Studio version projects folder. By default only projects from source Studio version projects folder are marked to be moved.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value: By selecting this option the translation memories navigation pane from the destination Studio version will be updated with the translation memories from the source Studio version. Translation Memories will physically remain in the same place on your machine.
